te><br />\n咁例如有時人地問一陣想做咩嗰時使唔使考慮埋人地嘅諗法？<br />\n抑或係照講自己想點？"},{"pid":"a9cf3fee75b9be204708f806bd5307293f6e151a","tid":496470,"uid":144977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:25:17.000Z","msg":"好多時就係因為諗太多<br />\n我都好想改左佢<br />\n但唔諗多啲又好唔安落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1764b45104827984099ca0cb1bf6cf5b76b24d","tid":496470,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"男人老狗連自己想做啲乜都要出post 問人<br />\n點出黎溝女呀"},{"pid":"9d9d081ebf63cd0b1df9273587cc57c09fdad1e4","tid":496470,"uid":69931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"究竟你幾時先肯開始罷食M記？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3c55866160c78f8c499a3bc8f4ebf2acf2fb3b","tid":496470,"uid":72519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗連自己想做啲乜都要出post 問人<br />\n點出黎溝女呀</blockquote><br />\n所以依家咪出post搵辦法改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98aeac3b0e76947e340655442b75cccb55ea59d1","tid":496470,"uid":118642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:24:46.000Z","msg":"好乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a61bcd78eeeb04dbe9f482d0ce7891993b52cb","tid":496470,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試下逼自己所有野都要5秒做決定,5秒入面揀唔到都要求其揀</blockquote><br />\n會唔會好易做錯決定？</blockquote><br />\n仆街仆得多下次唔使諗都識揀啦"},{"pid":"fd1496d873638ab0e12cedc6622d27de48c2f40e","tid":496470,"uid":101022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下逼自己所有野都要5秒做決定,5秒入面揀唔到都要求其揀</blockquote><br />\n會唔會好易做錯決定？</blockquote><br />\n仆街仆得多下次唔使諗都識揀啦</blockquote><br />\n小弟自己都係咁既人，中學個時用小息成日買野食都要讓畀後面十個人買完我自諗到。<br />\n大個都覺得自己好煩膠，自此我同人出街多數會尻揀，或者話諗唔到有無好介紹，如果同女出街就要一早諗定，或許都係尻揀。得番自己一個先慢慢諗要啲咩。"},{"pid":"f5bfa008730a06a24c3122c52ef3db6a3920c334","tid":496470,"uid":8598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:48:08.000Z","msg":"無傷大雅嘅事，諗到做乜就做啦<br />\n<br />\n利申，好憎唔嗲唔吊嘅人"},{"pid":"4ab268dcb4cc6213ac100fdc06f947da0f19f230","tid":496470,"uid":72519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"308cea005f3df8f16a19d4d8be31b727e883d04f","tid":496470,"uid":72519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:53:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日都因為呢個問題比老母話乞人憎<br />\n已經聽慣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833c77dce51c5dc435a2a185e5a8a5dc19202800","tid":496470,"uid":100391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下逼自己所有野都要5秒做決定,5秒入面揀唔到都要求其揀</blockquote><br />\n會唔會好易做錯決定？</blockquote><br />\n自己衡量下先囉<br />\n好多野無關大雅,揀錯野食最多肚屙接受到個結果就是旦揀,呢類通常都係私人野。<br />\n有d錯左大大獲,寧願你唔揀都好過你揀錯<br />\n呢d應該係工作事多。</blockquote><br />\n假如大事上要做決定咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵個男人照顧你 幫你揸主意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人頂得順喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要搵個大男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d3a22b4c9edf398eb64509c30cb83fadf31db7","tid":496470,"uid":72519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T11:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下逼自己所有野都要5秒做決定,5秒入面揀唔到都要求其揀</blockquote><br />\n會唔會好易做錯決定？</blockquote><br />\n自己衡量下先囉<br />\n好多野無關大雅,揀錯野食最多肚屙接受到個結果就是旦揀,呢類通常都係私人野。<br />\n有d錯左大大獲,寧願你唔揀都好過你揀錯<br />\n呢d應該係工作事多。</blockquote><br />\n假如大事上要做決定咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵個男人照顧你 幫你揸主意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人頂得順喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要搵個大男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港邊有咁多大男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s.仲以為個post沉咗底唔會有人回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b757fbfc727723cfd27781d4ab5f7ac0a914932","tid":496470,"uid":136015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T17:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗下自己最後會揀啲咩，個個就係你心之所向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁例如有時人地問一陣想做咩嗰時使唔使考慮埋人地嘅諗法？<br />\n抑或係照講自己想點？</blockquote><br />\n照自己講想點啦，人地唔啱就會講嘅，之後你可以就人或者同人討論下邊個選擇好啲 講下自己個選擇有咩好 話唔定人地會比你說服到呢！一切好隨意 今次做唔到咪下次做 冇所謂嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25f1e0c0e7b647ceaa885b2d894686f494a998d","tid":496470,"uid":115537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}